race.description: Ladbrokes Spring Hosted Pots Mdn Plate
race.comment: ALPINE COWGIRL (6) is a former Victorian who got too far back freshened for the new stable. Her better form reads well and she will get every chance with Pires staying aboard. Go close in this suitable assignment. WHO'S IN DEV (8) will be better for the two placed efforts on the synthetic. Raced as the favourite last time and maps for a soft run. RAPIDS AHEAD (3) drifted well back from the inside draw last time before winding up strongly beaten 2.3L on the Synthetic. Peaks and is sure to prove tough to stop. I'M A MACHINE (1) ran a better race last start beaten 1.2L on the synthetic. Ready to make his presence felt.
